              We continuously monitor performance metrics and use data insights to optimize campaigns for better results and higher ROI.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#D89D40] to-[#FE9002] text-white rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg mr-6 shadow-lg">
